UID:event_313931312@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260327T015650Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T150000
SUMMARY:KHTA Adopters and Mainteners Work Day - April 4
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\n**KHTA Volunteers & Adopters Workdays – April 4**\n\nWe have made considerable progress since the beginning of the year clearing trail\, building drains\, and chainsawing blowdowns from mile 34 to mile 35.5 (Hwy 56). We will continue maintenance of the trail on the North side of Highway 56\nDetails will be posted here\, on Meetup\, and Facebook. We will continue to meet on the North side of Hwy 56 at the trail crossing.\nWe will park at the trail crossing of North Level Road Ratt Road. From the Elk Creek Lake entrance head west up the hill for about 1.3 miles. For Google directions click on [Highway 56 Trail Crossing](https://maps.app.goo.gl/Pm8WyrtSzUbcerDk9)\nPlease bring a lunch and water. We will have large hand tools\, you may bring any small tools you have such as clippers or a pruning saw. And a backpack is handy to carry everything in. Instructions will be provided for those who need them. We will finish at about 3:00.\nSign up on [Meetup](https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of-indiana-meetup/events/312393553/?eventOrigin=group_upcoming_events)\nJoin us on our website at [http://www.knobstonehikingtrail.org/](http://www.knobstonehikingtrail.org/) and on Facebook at [KHTA Facebook Group.](https://www.facebook.com/groups/2255586117953484/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of-indiana-meetup/events/313931312/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260324T202554Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260324T202554Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/2/1/1/600_451380529.jpeg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_312918119@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260327T015650Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T091500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T151500
SUMMARY:2nd Weekend Work Day Trail Building
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\nWould you to spend a day in some beautiful woods with a delightful group of people building a connecting section of Indiana’s premier long distance hiking trail? Come join us as we continue work on the Tecumseh Trail extension portion of the KHT in MMSF. We will be building the new trail including clipping green briar.\nPlease bring a lunch and water. We will have large hand tools\, but please bring any small tools you have such as clippers or a pruning saw. And a backpack is handy to carry everything in. Instructions will be provided for those who need them. We finish about 3:30.\nMeet at the Hatfield Ridge Road gate. The gate is locked but we have a key. Go to the big sign on Rosenbaum/Catholic Cemetry Rd.\nJoin us on our website at http://www.knobstonehikingtrail.org/\, on Facebook at [www.facebook.com/groups/2255586117953484](http://www.facebook.com/groups/2255586117953484)\, and Substack [https://khta.substack.com/](https://khta.substack.com/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of-indiana-meetup/events/312918119/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260116T195304Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T195304Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/2/1/1/600_451380529.jpeg
END:VEVENT
